old castle,Dorn Bulgoth,was taken by
unknown intruders. They had masks and
cloaks. My soldiers fought bravely,but
we lost. The indruders had magic. I
think they are causing my subjects to
go mad. If you can kill their leader
and bring back his head as proof. I
will reward you.
endmsg
